author: thomreis
body:
This PR includes PR #15388 and has the DQM related commits of PR #15378 cherry-picked on top of it.

After testing, commit https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/commit/825dbe69b1c3c8c7614de2cce46a227143a4198a was added to fix a ProductNotFound.

This should supersede PRs #16502 and #15378.
title: L1 muon DQM for CMSSW_8_0_23
